Artificial Life Simulation - Greenies and Blueies - javascript version
===========================================================================

About
-------

This is the javascript version of the  project in previously published in http://inf0warri0r.blogspot.com/2013/08/artificial-life-simulation-greenies-and.html by me. Itis to simulate two types of artificial life forms which can feed, grow and reproduce. The first type which resembles plants can reproduce and grow.  feed on first type.

for more info, go to the above link.

How to use
------------

Run the eco_sim.html on a browser. To make greenies click on the blak squear whin the 'Type' button says Greeny. To make bluies click the 'type' button to toggle it in to bluey and click on a greeny.

use '+' or '-' buttons to set the speed of the simulation.

